Expand the following (i) 25024<sub>6</sub> (ii) 10110<sub>2</sub> (iii) 4102<sub>5</sub> (iv) 2389<sub>10</sub> in powers of their bases.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Solution</strong>
<br>
<strong>Note:</strong> any number raised to power of zero is <strong>1.</strong>
<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col border-right border-danger">
    (i)
    <br>
    <strong><i>4 3 2 1 0 - powers</i></strong>
    <br>
    2 5 0 2 4<sub>6</sub>
    <br>
    = 2 x 6<sup>4</sup>  +  5 x 6<sup>3</sup> + 0 x 6<sup>2</sup> + 2 x 6<sup>1</sup> + 4 x 6<sup>0</sup>
    <br>
    = 2 x 6<sup>4</sup>  +  5 x 6<sup>3</sup> + 0 x 6<sup>2</sup> + 2 x 6<sup>1</sup> + 4 x 1
    </div>
    <div class="col">
    (ii)
    <br>
    <strong><i>4 3 2 1 0 – powers</i></strong>
    <br>
    1 0 1 1 0<sub>2</sub>
    <br>
    = 1 x 2<sup>4</sup> + 0 x 2<sup>3</sup> + 1 x 2<sup>2</sup> + 1 x 2<sup>1</sup> + 0 x 2<sup>0</sup>
    <br>
    = 1 x 2<sup>4</sup> + 0 x 2<sup>3</sup> + 1 x 2<sup>2</sup> + 1 x 2<sup>1</sup> + 0 x 1
   </div>
  </div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col border-right border-danger">
    (iii)
    <br>
    <strong><i>3 2 1 0 – powers</i></strong>
     <br>
     4 1 0 2<sub>5</sub>
     <br>
     = 4 x 5<sup>3</sup> + 1 x 5<sup>2</sup> + 0 x 5<sup>1</sup> + 2 x 5<sup>0</sup>
     <br>
     = 4 x 5<sup>3</sup> + 1 x 5<sup>2</sup> + 0 x 5<sup>1</sup> + 2 x 1
    </div>
    <div class="col">
    (iv)
    <br>
    <strong><i>3 2 1 0 – powers</i></strong>
    <br>Solution
    2 3 8 9<sub>10</sub>
    <br>
    = 2 x 10<sup>3</sup> + 3 x 10<sup>2</sup> + 8 x 10<sup>1</sup> + 9 x 10<sup>0</sup>
    <br>
    = 2 x 10<sup>3</sup> + 3 x 10<sup>2</sup> + 8 x 10<sup>1</sup> + 9 x 1
     </div>
  </div>
