  <h3 class='text-dark justify-content-center'>Conversion from other Bases to Base Ten</h3>
  </div>
  <hr>
  <strong>Steps;</strong>
  <br>
(i)	Expand the number bases in the powers of their bases.
<br>
(ii)	Sum up the results in step (i) above to get the conversion.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Example 1</strong>
<br>
Convert the following bases to base ten (i) 11001<sub>2</sub> (ii) 2120<sub>3</sub> (iii) 231<sub>4</sub> (iv) 31<sub>8</sub>
<br>
<br>
<strong>Solution</strong>
<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col border-right border-danger">
    (i)
    <br>
    <strong><i>4 3 2 1 0 – powers</strong></i>
    <br>
    1 1 0 0 1<sub>2</sub>
    <br>
    = 1 x 2<sup>4</sup> + 1 x 2<sup>3</sup> + 0 x 2<sup>2</sup> + 0 x 2<sup>1</sup> + 1 x 2<sup>0</sup>
    <br>
     = 2<sup>4</sup> + 2<sup>3</sup> + 0 + 0 + 1 x 1
     <br>
     = 16 + 8 + 1
     <br>
    = 25
    <br>
    = 1 1 0 0 1<sub>2</sub> => <strong> 25 or 25<sub>10</sub></strong>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
    (ii)
    <br>
    <strong><i>3 2 1 0 – powers </strong></i>
    <br>
    2 1 2 0<sub>3</sub>
    <br>
    = 2 x 3<sup>3</sup> + 1 x 3<sup>2</sup> + 2 x 3<sup>1</sup> + 0 x 3<sup>0</sup>
    <br>
    = 2 x 27 + 1 x 9 + 2 x 3 + 0 x 1
    <br>
    = 54 + 9 + 6 + 0
    <br>
    = 69
    <br>
    2 1 2 0<sub>3</sub> => <strong>69 or 69<sub>10</sub></strong> 
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col border-right border-danger">
    (iii)
    <br>
    <strong><i>2 1 0 – powers</strong></i>
    <br>
    2 3 1<sub>4</sub>
    <br>
    = 2 x 4<sup>2</sup> + 3 x 4<sup>1</sup> + 1 x 4<sup>0</sup>
    <br>
    = 2 x 16 + 3 x 4 + 1 x 1
    <br>
    = 32 + 12 + 1
    <br>
    = 45
    <br>
    2 3 1<sub>4</sub> => <strong>45 or 45<sub>10</sub></strong>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
    (iv)
    <br>
    <strong><i>1 0 – powers </strong></i>
    <br>
    3 1<sub>8</sub>
    <br>
    = 3 x 8<sup>1</sup> + 1 x 8<sup>0</sup>
    <br>
    = 3 x 8 + 1 x 1
    <br>
    = 24 + 1
    <br>
    = 25
    <br>
    31<sub>8</sub> => 25 or 25<sub>10</sub>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
